	<AbilityDef ParentName="RI_PsycastBase">
		<defName>RI_Ability_Resurrect</defName>
		<label>Resurrect</label>
		<description>&lt;color=#28BD75&gt;This technique is learned by the ElixirsStrengthen method in the Master Realm\n\n&lt;/color&gt;Qi cost440\n\nA feat that only top-level alchemists could master, using Qi to perfectly replicate a freshly dead corpse, even the cells were completely reorganized to bring the dead back to life.</description>
